{
  "chapter": 153,
  "chapter_summary": "第153章\"舌战青楼\"发生在曼清院的英雄宴上。寇仲与宋玉致在三楼走廊私会，宋玉致警告寇仲南海派高手晃公错正应李密之邀来洛阳，李密已向宋缺保证不会让寇仲兄弟活着离开。寇仲不以为意，回到厢房后与跋锋寒、徐子陵会合。\n\n寇仲当众揭露上官龙是阴癸派卧底，引发多方势力对峙。上官龙被迫现身应战，寇仲以\"十招之内迫其露出马脚\"为赌注。曲傲试图介入，被跋锋寒拦住。长白双凶符真、符彦与李天凡亦在场虎视眈眈。独孤凤、淳于薇、刘黑闼、邢一飞、祈八州等各方人物纷纷登场。\n\n本章展现了寇仲的智谋与胆识，通过舌战挑起上官龙的斗志，为接下来的决战铺垫。各方势力齐聚曼清院，局势一触即发。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "为何明知我在隔邻，也不过来见我？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我怕惹你生气，想先看看风头火势吧！嘿！玉…嘿！宋小姐你清减了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这段日子我的心情确不大好。却与你寇仲毫无关系，唉！为何坏人的命总比好人长呢？至少你寇仲仍未死！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "已有这么多人想我死了，宋小姐为何仍不怕人挤，还要来揍热闹？宋三小姐若憎厌我，只要一句话说出来就够了。我的脸皮虽不算薄，但仍是有一定的厚度。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我不是憎厌你，而是恨你。恨你无端端的来扰乱人家的心。现在摆明洛阳迟早会落到李密手上，而我则须依约嫁入李家，你是因此不敢来见我吧？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "洛阳一天未落入李密的手中事情仍未算数。我担心的却是令尊翁'天刀'宋缺他老人家。由于我出身寒微，纵使我发掘出宝藏，都不肯招我作女婿。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "竟陵一战后，谁能不对你和徐子陵刮目相看。以杜伏威之能，兵员之众，仍给你们领着残军硬拒于残破城垣之外逾十日之久。故问题非是在我爹身上，而是我根本不想嫁给你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "你先前说的一番话，显是对我大有情意，难道都是假的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "男人是否都像你般对女人没有开窍似的；又或总是粗心大意，自以为是。若我不把你放在心上，和你多说半句话都不愿意。你可知为何我要唤你出来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "是呢！究竟是为了甚么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "因为人家想看你是否比前更成熟了。而更重要的是希望你不要再去惹李密，还须有那么远躲那么远。因为据我们得的秘密消息，南海派的元老高手晃公错正应李密之邀，在来洛阳的途上。到时第一个遭殃的将是你两兄弟。李密已向我爹保证不会让你两人活着离开洛阳。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "晃公错是甚么家伙和东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若要在中原挑十个武功最强横的人出来，晃公错必可入选，甚或在五名之内。你现在知道了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "这天下不会是一成不变的。朝代也会更换，更何况高手的位置？在以前随便找个人出来也可打得我们一仆一跌的日子已不复再，你看我们仍不是活得好好的。这晃老头不会比阴癸派更厉害吧？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们曾惹上阴癸派吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "不是惹上了，而是正斗个你死我活。否则今晚我也不会见到你。嘻！可否对我说句较好听的话。那我纵是死了，也可带着一片美丽甜蜜的回忆到阴间去做鬼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "本小姐永远都不会说违心的话。人家的警告你不听就算，我走啦！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不要扯手扯脚，传了出去，爹说不定会派人杀你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "信不信由你，你等着嫁我吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大言不惭，不知死活！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "符真",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这叫天堂有路你不走，地狱无门却闯进来。小子你不找个鼠洞躲起来，却要学现在般招摇而过，是否活得不耐烦了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_zhen",
      "text": "你们不知王薄今晚在此吗？若不趁早夹着尾巴落荒而逃，恐怕连李密都护你们不住哩！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "符真",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "好小子！竟知道我们是谁，既是如此，当知我们谁也不怕，为何还说出如许胡言。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_zhen",
      "text": "既是甚么人都不怕，就不用从长白逃到这里来。就让寇某人试试你们手底的功夫是否和你嘴皮子那么硬吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "speaker_name": "李天凡",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你刚才和李某的未过门妻子说了些甚么话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "text": "这里所有姐姐妹妹都是我寇仲未过门的妻子，不知李兄说的是那一位呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "独孤凤",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "胡说八道。谁是你的妻子。你这种人谁肯嫁你？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_feng",
      "text": "独孤凤小姐说得好，若未过门都算是妻子，那岂非天下大乱了吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_man_qing_yuan_nan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曼清院男子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李公子和两位符老师请给我们曼清院一点面子，有甚么事到院外再处理吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "给我看看脸上是否多了宋三小姐的掌印。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "刚才我在外面闹得曼清院都差点塌下来，你两个仍不出来援手，还说甚么一世人两兄弟。唉！这就叫人情冷暖，世态炎凉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲少你动过那只手呢？若只是舌战，你何需别人助拳。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们正希望他们动手，所以故意避而不出，让他们更没有顾忌。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我也只是说说笑。咦！刚才我们说到那里呢？美女真不好，最易令人忘记事情的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不要装蒜了，你究竟想到甚么对付上官龙的妙计呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！终于记起了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "text": "上官龙何在！祝玉妍拣得你作阴癸派在洛阳的卧底，应该会有两下子，可敢立即上来决一死战！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "speaker_name": "上官龙",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只是你如此含血喷人，我上官龙便绝不会放过你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "text": "我们这里有三个人，任你挑那一个都行。但这种特别优待，只会赠给阴癸派的妖人，皆因人人都得而诛之。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_ao",
      "speaker_name": "曲傲",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这叫踏破铁鞋无觅处，得来全不费工夫。寇小子和徐小子你两人一起下来吧！既可省我分两次动手，又可作大战前的热身。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_qu_ao",
      "text": "曲傲你已是我跋锋寒的。却想有像上官帮主的优待，那怎么成？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_ao",
      "speaker_name": "曲傲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋锋寒你今晚若有命离开曼清院，我曲傲两字以后就倒转来写。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_qu_ao",
      "text": "这真是奇哉怪也。上趟老曲你单对单仍没有能力收拾锋寒兄，为何现在又忽然有了？是否感到把名宇掉转来写较有新鲜感儿。不过现在仍未是轮到你老兄出手的时候，因为刚才我猜拳猜赢了跋锋寒，故而上官帮主该抽到头筹。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "符真",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "曲老师可怜你们年少无知，故此放你三人一马，仍不知感激，实是可笑之极。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_zhen",
      "text": "符老师你的隐身功夫定比你追不上人的失踪术高明万倍，否则为何以老曲和老跋两人的修为，仍不知你在旁窥伺，连'年少无知'这种微妙的情况都看个明察秋毫。谁人敢不服你！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "说得好，我刘黑闼心中有个疑问，就是为何寇兄认为上官帮主另一个秘密身份乃阴癸派的妖人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "speaker_name": "上官龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "清者自清，若再有人以此来诬蔑本人，休怪我上官龙不留情脸。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "邢一飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "text": "既是清者自清，为何又怕人说出来？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xing_yi_fei",
      "text": "这才真是说得好。这位朋友高姓大名，说出来看上官帮主敢否寻你晦气？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "邢一飞",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "本人邢一飞，乃伏骞王子的首席先锋将，比他早到一步，上官帮主请勿忘记了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "text": "在尚小姐的好戏开锣前，上官帮主有没有意思和小弟先玩一场，为四方君子解解闷儿？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_yu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "淳于薇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "说得真动听，寇仲你是最讨我欢喜的哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又来了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_ba_zhou",
      "speaker_name": "祈八州",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本人乃'洛阳八士'的祈八州，今次知世郎在听留阁举行英雄宴，一切安排打点，全由老夫负责。王公既然未到，老夫该有资格说两句话吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "text": "时间无多，上官龙你是否仍要做缩头乌龟？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "这小子恁地威风，竟抢了锋寒兄的头筹。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若我是上官龙，怎都不会迎战。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "speaker_name": "上官龙",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你说我是阴癸派的人，究竟有何凭据。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "text": "要证据还不容易，若我十招之内，仍未能迫得上官帮主露出马脚，寇某愿向帮主斟茶认错。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "仲少似乎把话说得太满了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "我们的功夫是给迫出来的，仲少定有他的一套。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_long",
      "speaker_name": "上官龙",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你勿要赖账，动手吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 412
    }
